On Wednesday we were at @darwin.camp to celebrate the launch of the VEJA x @seashepherd collaboration.
We gave a talk called “Are we eating the planet?” in front of 400 people. 
This was hosted by: 
@lamyass, president of @seashepherd @graine_de_possible, social and climate justice activist 
@sebastien_kopp, co-founder of VEJA 
@philippebarre, founder of @darwin.camp 
@missno, journalist. 

We talked about the Amazon, overfishing, and actions and non-actions. We discussed the effectiveness of climate marches…and much more! 

